text: Ærest of crawan crundul on wereðan hylle.
On ðon harepoðe to headdan grafe.
Ðonne on ðone hagan to wytan wyrðe.
On ða dic et Hiceles wyrðe.
Ðonne ofer ðone feld on hagan ut þurh bremberwudu on ðone stenenan stapul.
Andlang herepaðes to ðes hagan ende to fegerhilde forda.
On ðone hagan on Ceorles hlewe, on crawan crundul.
Ðonne on ða yferan gemere on Eblesburnan.
Andlang weges on ða dic to bymera cumbe.
And ðer þwyres ofer þreo crundelas ofer ða streat.
Ðæt þurch ofer ða done to wudu beorch hylle ofer berigancumb on Eblesburnan.
Ofer higcumb on ðan smalan wege on ðone stan, on ðet heð westeweard on ðone beorch to ðem ricgwege.
Ðonne east andlang hricgweges to Brytfordinga landsceare.
Ðis is ðæs landes boc et Duntune ðe æðelræd cynyg edniwan gebocodæ sanctæ trinitati and sanctæ Pætre and Paulæ into Ealdan mynstran.
